About

I am a graduate from the University of Washington with a double degree in physics and astronomy. I worked as a web engineer at a graphic design firm for two years before begining freelance work.

Music is an integral part of my life and I've been playing piano and guitar for over ten years. I also enjoy cooking, comedy, video and computer games, bicycling, and tennis.
